article_title: Obamacare Will Usher In A Two-Tiered Health Care System

article_metadata.description: Providing people with insurance does not mean that a doctor will see you. The Affordable Care Act will lead to separate health care systems where your access to doctors depends on the generosity of your insurance.
article_metadata.author: Jeffrey Dorfman
